                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For a reference to an estimate of Soviet intentions by the American Embassy in
                    Moscow, April 1, see <hi rend="italic">The Forrestal Diaries</hi>, edited by
                    Walter Millis (New York, The Viking Press, 1951), <ref target="#pg_409">page
                        409</ref>. For related documentation see the compilation on United States
                    National Security Policy in <ref target="frus1948v01p1">volume I</ref>.</p>
            </div>
